Simple features

Functions used to return simple features (sf) objects of the Dominican Republic administrative boundaries.

Load Dominican Republic Sections Simple Features (sf)
dr_municipal_districts()
Load Dominican Republic Municipal Districts Simple Features (sf)
dr_municipalities()
Load Dominican Republic Municipalities Simple Features (sf)
dr_provinces()
Load Dominican Republic Provinces Simple Features (sf)
get_dr_provinces()
Deprecated function: get_dr_provinces
dr_regions()
Load Dominican Republic Development Regions Simple Features (sf)
